    All Classes and Interfaces

    Classes
    Class
    Description
    AgeGroup
    Represents the population data for a specific age group.
    AgeGroupCombiner
    A utility class responsible for combining smaller age groups into broader age categories.
    ApiCodes
    The ApiCodes class is a Spring component that holds mappings for various codes related to countries, movies, genres, and indicators.
    CombinedDataByYear
    Represents a combined data object for a specific year, containing information about a country, genre, population statistics, and the number of movies released.
    DataCombiner
    A service class responsible for combining movie and population data into a unified data structure.
    DataController
    The DataController class handles API requests related to combining movie and population data, as well as managing user preferences.
    MoviePopularityBackendApplication
    The main class for the Movie Popularity Backend application.
    MovieStatistics
    Represents movie statistics for a specific genre, year, and country.
    PopulationStatistics
    Represents the population data for a specific country and year.
    SaveService
    Service for saving and fetching user preference data into a json file
    TmdbService
    Service for interacting with the TMDB (The Movie Database)
    UnPopulationService
    Service with methods for fetching population data from the UN API.
    UserPreferences
    Represents a single user preference for graph settings in the front end
    Utility
    This is an utility class with methods for parsing data, and other future possible utility methods.
    WebConfig
    Configuration class for setting up CORS (Cross-Origin Resource Sharing) settings accross the whole application.
